  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.3">
<l>māyō ṉikaḷāy naṭaikaṟṟa vāṉōr palaru muṉivaru</l>
<l>nīyō ṉikaḷaip paṭaiyeṉṟu niṟaināṉ mukaṉaip paṭaittavaṉ</l>
<l>cēyō ṉellā vaṟivukkun ticaika ḷellān tiruvaṭiyā</l>
<l>ṟāyō ṉellā vevvuyirkkun tāyōṉ ṟāṉō ruruvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who created the one with four faces, saying “you create the wombs</l>
<l>for the sages and many of the immortals who learned to walk as great wombs”,</l>
<l>the one who is distant, the one extended his holy feet over all the directions</l>
<l>for all knowledge, the one who expanded all living beings, he is of one form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
